00:30:10,574 --> 00:30:12,166
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That is disgusting!

449
00:30:13,544 --> 00:30:17,412
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- We told you not to break that egg. - Now look what you've done, rat!

