00:53:56,065 --> 00:53:57,430
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Don't slow down yet.

782
00:54:23,092 --> 00:54:25,822
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Welcome to Zuckerman's! Thank you all for coming.

