00:54:35,671 --> 00:54:39,664
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And for that reason, l've decided to enter Wilbur into the county fair.

786
00:54:43,979 --> 00:54:47,346
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Did you hear what they said, Charlotte? I'm going to the fair!

787
00:54:47,750 --> 00:54:48,910
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Going to the fair!

