00:54:49,018 --> 00:54:51,179
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Wilbur might just see Christmas after all.

789
00:54:51,287 --> 00:54:52,618
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Is it good? Did we do it?

790
00:54:52,722 --> 00:54:54,713
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Yes, Wilbur. It's very good.

791
00:54:54,957 --> 00:54:56,447
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Now, smile.

792
00:54:56,559 --> 00:54:59,585
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The fair, Homer? What's gotten into you?

793
00:54:59,695 --> 00:55:01,458
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I don't know, Sis. It just come to me.

