00:55:05,868 --> 00:55:09,201
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That spider did a heck of a job. She's a hard worker.

797
00:55:09,305 --> 00:55:12,172
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Thank you, Charlotte. You should take a little bow.

798
00:55:12,274 --> 00:55:14,333
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And have my beauty steal the show?

799
00:55:14,443 --> 00:55:17,412
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Now, go on and show them what a radiant pig can do.

