00:55:29,425 --> 00:55:31,325
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What do you mean you're not going to the fair?

801
00:55:31,427 --> 00:55:34,658
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm going to get a prize. Don't you want to be there?

