00:56:12,434 --> 00:56:13,901
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Fern? - Mom!

813
00:56:15,471 --> 00:56:16,938
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm not wearing that.

