00:56:33,856 --> 00:56:35,687
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Bathed in buttermilk.

816
00:56:43,232 --> 00:56:44,893
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I've had this dream.

