00:56:50,406 --> 00:56:53,500
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I've got to say he really is some pig.

818
00:56:53,876 --> 00:56:55,844
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That's my buttermilk working.

819
00:56:56,145 --> 00:56:58,136
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You sure you want to go through with this, Homer?

820
00:56:58,247 --> 00:57:00,545
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}If you lose, you're out your entry fee.

